      "expected_output": "The response uses the Workbench CLI skill eval-authoring docs, starts from the existing-workflow guide, writes a hosted `workbench.yaml`, wraps the existing command in runner/grader phases where the grader writes `WORKBENCH_REWARD_FILE` with a finite `score`, and uses `workbench check`, `workbench sync`, and a hosted smoke workflow.",
      "files": [],
